Use/Develop the SVN directory:
1) Copy oxygen-firefox-theme@oxygen-icons.org to your firefox profile's
   extension directory (e.g. /home/me/.mozilla/firefox/xxxxx.default/extensions)
2) Edit the file and add the path where the firefox/Oxygen/ folder is stored
3) Restart Firefox

Create a jar:
$ cd Oxygen
$ zip -r ../oxygen.jar *

Create a release tarball:
run the release script with the tarball version
$ ./release.rb 1.0
